msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "U-Um... Hey, Mister!\r\nCan I get a minute of your time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "There's something I need t'ask ya.\r\nWhat, um... What year is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Wellll, like, um...\r\nI wanna know what year it is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "It's 2016."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "2016? Y'mean it!?\r\nY'really really mean it!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Yesss! I actually did it!\r\nSo then... this is really a year in the past?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "And this is what I was like a year ago?\r\nOh yeah, my boobs are totally smaller now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "What? What the hell are you saying?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry about that.\r\nI went off on a tangent there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "The thing is, well... I just performed\r\na time leap from a year in the future!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "A time leap?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Yup! I'm actually from the year 2017!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "I don't understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Oh, did I not make it clear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Okeydokey! Let me start by explaining the\r\ndifference between time travel and a time leap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "(What is she talking about...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "A time leap is when your consciousness transfers\r\nfrom one point in time to your body in another time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "...Uh-huh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "As for time travel, it's more like when you\r\nmove through time with a machine or something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "For example, if a guy goes back a day in a time machine,\r\nboth him and the him from yesterday would be there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Basically two of the same guy would\r\nexist in the same place and time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "With a time leap, just his consciousness transfers\r\ninto his past body, so there's only one of him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Well? Do y'get it now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I think I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "In my case, my consciousness from 2017 has\r\ncome back a year to inhabit my 2016 body!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I didn't think I'd be able to leap a whole year!\r\nI'm pretty damn awesome, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Sure, I guess you could say that.\r\nWell, sorry for holding you up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Um, what? Don't leave!\r\nCome back, Mister!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I just made a pretty spectacular claim.\r\nDon't you like, have questions or something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Nah, I'm all right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Huh? Reallyyyyy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "If you insist.\r\nI guess I can stick around a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Yay, thanks Mister!\r\nOh, and my name's Miku."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "I'm Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Gotcha! Kiryu-san, right?\r\nI'm gonna go out on a limb here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "...But you don't believe I actually\r\ntime leaped just now, do ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "You mean how you came back here from\r\nthe future? Of course I don't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Then how can I convince ya\r\nI'm telling the truth?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm not sure you can.\r\nHmmm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Actually, if you're really from 2017,\r\nyou know the future, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Does anything strange happen in the next year?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Strange? So like, something major?\r\nHm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "It's hard t'think of examples on the spot.\r\nCan y'ask me something specific?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "If I have to. Let's see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Are there gonna be any serious natural disasters?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Ummm, I don't <font_kind=yakuza_italic>think</font_kind> so...?\r\nThere might be a few earthquakes..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Oh, there was one pretty interesting disaster!\r\nMy mom totally ran over my dad with her car."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "He came out of it totally fine...\r\nbut ugh, my dad's so lame."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Hold on, I don't care about your family issues.\r\nI want to know what the papers write about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "C'mon, nobody reads the papers nowadays.\r\nWe get news through our phones."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah! We have these fancy things\r\ncalled smartphones in 2017!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "They were around in 2016, too..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Oh, yeah. I guess you're right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Can you tell me who'll win the big horse races?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Oh, that makes sense! That would prove\r\nI came from the future for sure!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "I didn't think of it this time...\r\nbut I'll definitely remember for my next time leap!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Thanks a bunch!\r\nYour idea's gonna make me real rich, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Wait, your next time leap?\r\nThat doesn't prove anything here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Huhhh? But I can't answer your question now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Where will I be a year from now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "How am I s'posed to know that?\r\nI only just met ya, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Oh, maybe I could time leap forward a year!\r\nThen I'd be able t'tell ya the answer!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Although, it might be hard telling you the truth\r\nif things go south for you. Like if you die..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "That's fine.\r\nJust tell me whatever you see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "You're so calm about this.\r\nI guess you don't believe in me at all, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Hold on a sec. I just realized, nothing you say\r\ncan really prove you're from the future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Don't you have any physical proof?\r\nSomething that's definitely from 2017?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Uhhh... Like, a newspaper dated in the future?\r\nOr maybe a 100 yen coin?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Yeah, that would be more convincing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "I already told you though,\r\nonly my consciousness came back here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "So you can't prove it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "My words should be proof enough.\r\nJust look me in the eyes and say you believe me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "All right, I believe you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Huh? You mean it!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Come on. You can't expect that to work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Huh? But I told you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "I will say though, you don't really seem\r\nlike the kind of girl who'd pull a trick like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Ah, so you <font_kind=yakuza_italic>do</font_kind> believe me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "This would go on forever if I didn't.\r\nI don't have that kind of time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "That's kinda rude..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Either way, you have a reason for coming back\r\nto 2016, right? I should get out of your hair."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "You know, you're actually pretty cute."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Huh? Where'd that come from?\r\nAlthough, I'm kinda into older guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Even though I'm probably older than your father?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "My dad? I don't wanna think about him now. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "But... you might really be older than him, Kiryu-san.\r\nUgh, I'm just thinking of his face now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Teenagers really can't stand their parents, huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Heck no..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I should get going.\r\nI really don't have time to waste."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "What about the time leap?\r\nI guess you don't believe in it, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Yup. Time's up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "Besides, if you really <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> telling the truth,\r\nyou must have a reason to be back in 2016."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "I shouldn't keep you from it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "I actually don't have a reason."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "I only discovered my time leap power\r\na couple of days ago, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "I've been trying t'figure out where I got it,\r\nbut my search has come up empty so far."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "So, I decided to test out a few time leaps\r\nto see what my limits were!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "In that case, let me know if you learn anything.\r\nSee you later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Huhhh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Hey Mister, can we talk about my time leap?\r\nI wanna prove I'm not just messing with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Wanna let me explain in a bit more detail?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "What do I do...?\r\nI'm gonna be stuck here forever..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Hey, what's wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Huh? \r\nOh, it's you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Remember me? Miku!\r\nI'm the time leaper..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Of course I remember.\r\nWhat's wrong? Why the tears?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Um, it's a kinda long story.\r\nDo y'wanna listen, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Nah, maybe some other time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Right. You must be busy, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Of course. I wouldn't just abandon you.\r\nSo go on, let's hear what you have to say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Um, well... The thing is...\r\nI... I lost my time leap powers!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "...Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "I knew it.\r\nYou still don't believe me, do you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "I'm not lying t'ya, though!\r\nI really <font_kind=yakuza_italic>can</font_kind> leap through time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Let's suppose you can, then.\r\nHow exactly do you do it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "I just close my eyes and think back to\r\na moment I wanna revisit. That's all it takes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "My first time leap was right after\r\nI said something really horrible to my dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "I wanted t'take back what I said, so I prayed.\r\nPrayed that I could go back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "What exactly did you say to him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Well, my dad's really lame. He doesn't have any\r\nself-confidence, and barely even acts like a dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Because of that, my mom...\r\nShe started cheatin' on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "The family was falling apart. My dad knew about\r\nthe affair, but was too afraid t'say anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Then one humid day, my mom was out neglecting\r\nour family again. Probably was out with her boytoy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "I got a bad grade on a test that day, too.\r\nAnd on top of that, the sink was totally busted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "That's when... I snapped. I took it all out on my dad,\r\neven though my mom was the real problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "I blamed him for mom's affair.\r\nCalled him a coward for not confronting her..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "And my dad just sat there crying. All because of me...\r\nBut that just made it harder t'stop!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "I get it. That stuff's not easy for a kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "That's when I leapt back to before I yelled at him.\r\nThis time I didn't say any of that stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "I'm really glad I got a redo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "I've been obsessed with time leaps since then.\r\nI couldn't stop reading sci-fi books from the library."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "They helped me forget about how sad my life was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "But now for some reason...\r\nmy time leap power's totally gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "What can I do?\r\nIf I'm stuck here, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "Look, Miku.\r\nI'm not so sure this is a problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "You only went a year into the past.\r\nCan't you just wait until you're back in 2017?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Well, I'd normally agree with you.\r\nBut..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "...I can't go through all of that again!\r\nI can't stand another year with my dad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Miku... I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Heyyy! Miku!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Ah... Dad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Hey, I'm just headin' on home now.\r\nY'wanna come with?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "Uh, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "Who's this fella?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Oh, this is Kiryu-san.\r\nI only just met him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "I'm Kiryu. Don't worry,\r\nI'll make sure your daughter gets back safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "\r\nWill y'now? Ah, that's awful nice.\r\nHope she ain't causin' ya trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Anyway Miku, I'm hittin' the road.\r\nMom says she's cookin' up a feast tonight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Your story doesn't add up. Your dad seems fine,\r\nand it sounds like he gets along with your mom, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah... This is before everything changed..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "I remember now!\r\nDad! Don't go that way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Dad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Oh, my apologies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "What the!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Owwwwww! Man that hurts!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Huh? But, I didn't mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "Ya broke my arm, ya piece o' shit!\r\nIt's gonna cost ya, y'hear? Ugh, it hurts!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "Please, um... Please forgive me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Get down on yer knees n' beg!\r\nI ain't gonna let you off that easy, y'hear!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "No... I've seen this happen before.\r\nThey made Dad kneel down to them, and then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "A-Ahhh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Don't worry, Miku. What you're about to see\r\nis probably different from the future you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Hey, keep your hands off him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Huh? N' who're you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "I'm the one who's going to change history.\r\nNow if you're done talking... Bring it on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Can you hear me out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "It's kinda a long story...\r\nbut I wanna talk about time leaps again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much, Kiryu-san.\r\nHistory's been changed because of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "What originally happened was, those thugs forced\r\nmy dad to kneel and then they just beat on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "They totally humiliated him here on this bridge.\r\nMy dad probably didn't want me t'see him like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "I'm sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "He was always so cheerful, but from that day on,\r\nhe wouldn't even look me in the eye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "That's when things got bad at home, too.\r\nHe and my mom barely talked after that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "They used t'be so close..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "So thanks to your time leap, you managed\r\nto rewrite some bitter history?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "Yup. If I had t'guess, I'd say that's why\r\nI got my powers in the first place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "Well, Kiryu-san? Do you believe my story?\r\nDo you think I really leapt through time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "No way.\r\nYour word is all I have to go on, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "Geez, you don't trust me at all!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure if the power to redo the past\r\nreally exists in this world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "You only get one chance at life. You're born once,\r\nand you die once. The same applies to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "But you can change the middle as much as you want.\r\nDon't forget that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san.\r\nIs there anything you'd wanna do over?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure. I try to let the past\r\nstay in the past. That's how it works for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "Well, if I <font_kind=yakuza_italic>do</font_kind> manage to time leap again,\r\nI'll come prove it to you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Tell me what happens in the races, then.\r\nIf you're right about that, I'll believe you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "Will do! Bye now, Kiryu-san!\r\nThank you so much for everything!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "No problem."
msgstr ""

